<TD WIDTH=460 VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<IMG SRC="/graphics/inverter.gif" ALT="Inverter.gif - 2.0 K" WIDTH=124 HEIGHT=101>
International Rectifier offers a full range of inverter type thyristors (SCRs) in a variety of popular industry-standard packages.  The fast 
turn-on and turn-off and low switching loss characteristics of these SCRs make them ideally suited for inverter and chopper circuit 
applications in UPS systems, induction heating, and DC and AC motor drives.  All devices rated above 135 amps (rms) use amplifying 
gate construction for high di/dt capability.  They also offer a guaranteed gate noise immunity.<br> Special inverter SCRs for high 
frequency operation are also available.  These devices offer an interdigitated gate configuration for faster turn-on and higher di/dt, 
while maintaining low switching losses.  For further information, contact your local IR <a href="whoto-call/salesrep/">sales 
representatives</a>.
</TR>
</TD>
